Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:16.16,ReSub,,0,0,0,,Rei-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:24.30,ReSub,,0,0,0,,Rei-chan, fatti forza!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:27.21,ReSub,,0,0,0,,Non perdere da quella Tanaka-san!
